937
00:45:46,942 --> 00:45:49,403
The surrounding area has also been searched upside down.

938
00:45:49,403 --> 00:45:50,882
There was no results at all.

939
00:45:50,882 --> 00:45:53,629
Now, he's preparing to search the campsite here.

940
00:45:54,929 --> 00:45:56,555
He really is going all out.

941
00:45:56,555 --> 00:45:58,598
He's not even afraid of disturbing Imperial Father.

942
00:45:58,598 --> 00:46:00,484
But he's come at just the right moment.

943
00:46:00,484 --> 00:46:02,753
I'll let him help me by acting as my witness.

944
00:46:02,753 --> 00:46:04,868
Eighth Prince is going to see the Crown Prince?

945
00:46:04,868 --> 00:46:06,284
How will you be able to hide your injury?

946
00:46:06,284 --> 00:46:07,870
Even if you're able to hide it tonight,

947
00:46:07,870 --> 00:46:09,663
